      "topic": "Formal - Confirming attendance",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "label": "Opening",
          "text": "Dear Conference Organizers, I am writing to confirm my attendance at the International Marketing Conference. Thank you for accepting my registration for the event on November 12th. I am pleased to confirm that I will be attending the symposium as planned."
        },
        {
          "label": "Main Content",
          "text": "I would like to confirm that I will be presenting during the afternoon session as scheduled. Could you please provide information about the presentation equipment that will be available? I will require a laptop connection and a microphone for my 30-minute presentation. Additionally, I would be grateful if you could send me details about the hotel accommodation arrangements. Would it be possible to receive a map of the venue in advance?"
        },
        {
          "label": "Closing",
          "text": "I look forward to participating in this prestigious event. Thank you for organizing what promises to be an excellent conference. Please contact me if you require any additional information. (Yours sincerely)"
        }
      ]
    },
