          "label": "Main Content",
          "text": "There's a lovely cottage by the lake that's available for Friday to Sunday. It sleeps six people comfortably and has a fireplace — perfect for cozy evenings! The cost is £300 for the weekend, which works out at £50 each if we get six people. I've already spoken to Emma and Jack and they're definitely up for it. We could leave Friday afternoon around 4pm to avoid traffic. Shall I go ahead and book it? I'll need everyone's share by Wednesday if we want to secure it. Let me know asap!"
        },
        {
          "label": "Closing",
          "text": "This is going to be so much fun! Get back to me when you can about the dates. Can't wait to spend quality time with everyone! Excited already! Chat soon, / Love, / Your enthusiastic friend,"
